summary: Fanfic idea: should I write it?
body:
Fanfic idea: should I write it?

AU where Tony Stark and Steve Rogers’ powers are switched.

Steve was meant to become the Super-Soldier, but the serum was not as effective as it should be: Steve became stronger, but not to a super human level and more like a skilled combatant. However, the experiments with the Tessaract came to a major breakthrough, and they managed to build a powerful sustainable power source similar to the arc reactor, leading to the development of a mechanical armor. However, the power source is ridiculously hard to manufacture and stabilize with wwii tech so only Steve had an armor because he happened to have the gifts for it. The plot of the first cap movie happened and Steve is sealed in ice but kept alive by the armor he had on.

The government believes the armors are the way to go (but the powersource tech was lost just like super soldier serum in canon) and the super soldier serum is a failed project. Howard Stark was however consumed by the development of the super soldier serum because he was wrapped up in the guilt that if the super soldier serum worked before Steve somehow wouldn’t have died. Young Tony’s idolization of Captain America actually is partially responsible for his fascination with machines. When Howard dies all his work on the super soldier serum was passed on to Tony, who after studying the formula roughly decided it wasn’t possible and isn’t worth the trouble so he tossed it aside.

When Tony was kidnapped, the terrorists demanded him to make some sort of biochemical weapon instead of missiles, therefore providing him with the materials that he used to improve the super soldier serum. His first working version of super soldier serum worked and got him out alive, but wasn’t very stable and needs to be improved and injected repeatedly over time kinda like his armor upgrades in canon. Then Cap was retrieved, along with his armor. How would things be different between them?

I feel like there is a lot of potential to this one and I can really explore these characters but I know it will be super long so I’m hesitant. I want to know if people will want to read it before I commit to such a huge project.

I’ll write it if it hits 30 notes.

Alright I’m going to write this. Might take forever tho lol.

by blood_and_gore

Stark died, out there in Siberia with nobody around and the knowlege of his parents’ deaths in his mind.

Elektra Natchios knows that death doesn’t have to be permanent. After all, she’s got half a dragon corpse stashed away. She’s alive and so is her beloved Matthew, thanks to it; therefore, it stands to reason she could use it to bring someone back. As soon as she figures out how.

Clint Barton has been mind controlled for two years. Nobody adjusts well from that.
